,Recommended,221260,47756,"Posted: 15 March, 2013",all,CriticalComposer,"An interesting little game that most likely will not appeal to all. There is no score or lives or difficutly. You burn items, which turn into coins, which you use to buy new items to burn. The cycle repeats as you continue buying new items to burn. The ending is well worth the couple of hours it takes to complete and there are secondary objectives in the form of ""combos"" where you have to burn two specific items at the same time. You have to find the combinations on your own though. All in all, this is a casual, fun, albeit repetitive game with a fantastic ending."
