,Recommended,221260,27512448,"Posted: 25 November, 2016",all,Die Potato ! [Altie],"Little Inferno... Well, quite an interesting game, based on BURN EVERYTHING YOU HAVE !!! You are a character, a ""whatever who he/she is personn"", there are some letters you receive from your neighbour, who seems at least as silly as you (seriously, you live your life in front your cheminee burning packages you just bought ?!?).Step by step, you understand that you are involved in a dystopian world, painted touch by touch, only by discrete clues... Your entire universe is limited to this cheminee, neighbour letter, news about weather, and your pad. In fact, I think this is the best madness metaphora ever made : you do anyway the same action, trying to do it better (why and how, this is YOUR problem) expecting something new to happen. And you will necessarly try to do all the combos you have to discover and unlock all the items to buy, because of... your sense of perfection maybe ?And finally (and after around 4 hours of playtime) something happens that totally change your vision of the game... Try it, be patient, and understand..."
